String.Source: Well, well, well, fancy meeting you out here... Overboss.
String.Dest: Well, well, well, fancy meeting you out here... Overboss.

String.Source: Oh, come on!
String.Dest: Ale no ták!

String.Source: I like your style. Save the fresh one for last.
String.Dest: I like your style. Save the fresh one for last.

String.Source: Do it! I've had enough of this world.
String.Dest: Do it! I've had enough of this world.

String.Source: No, please! I'll do anything!
String.Dest: No, please! I'll do anything!

String.Source: Ah, that's better. Now, let's get back to Nuka-World.
String.Dest: Ach, to je lepší. Nyní se vraťme do Nuka-Worldu.

String.Source: That ought to tide me over for a few days.
String.Dest: That ought to tide me over for a few days.

String.Source: I love it when they beg.
String.Dest: I love it when they beg.

String.Source: *sigh* All right. But... That doesn't mean I can't bleed them just a little.
String.Dest: *sigh* All right. But... That doesn't mean I can't bleed them just a little.

String.Source: The weak are always the first to go.
String.Dest: The weak are always the first to go.

String.Source: Of course it matters! One of these lucky fellas gets the privilege of watching the other die first.
String.Dest: Of course it matters! One of these lucky fellas gets the privilege of watching the other die first.

String.Source: Take the ghoul first.
String.Dest: Take the ghoul first.

String.Source: All right, ladies. Let's get started, shall we?
String.Dest: All right, ladies. Let's get started, shall we?

String.Source: You heard the boss. We can't kill 'em, but that doesn't mean we can't have a little fun first.
String.Dest: You heard the boss. We can't kill 'em, but that doesn't mean we can't have a little fun first.

String.Source: We were just debating which of these little lambs to bleed first. But since you're here, maybe you'd like the honor?
String.Dest: We were just debating which of these little lambs to bleed first. But since you're here, maybe you'd like the honor?

String.Source: Take the old man first.
String.Dest: Take the old man first.

String.Source: Way to steal a gal's fun, though I can't say I blame you.
String.Dest: Way to steal a gal's fun, though I can't say I blame you.

String.Source: Do it! I've had enough of this world.
String.Dest: Do it! I've had enough of this world.

String.Source: Didn't anyone ever tell you, "Never come between a gal and her prey?"
String.Dest: Copak ti nikdo neřekl, „nevstupuj mezi děvče a její kořist?“

String.Source: Let them live. We could use more workers in Nuka-World.
String.Dest: Let them live. We could use more workers in Nuka-World.

String.Source: No, please! I'll do anything!
String.Dest: No, please! I'll do anything!

String.Source: Does it really matter?
String.Dest: Opravdu na tom záleží?

String.Source: Hired ourselves a couple new additions to the Nuka-World... staff.
String.Dest: Hired ourselves a couple new additions to the Nuka-World... staff.

String.Source: You've got to be kidding me.
String.Dest: To si ze mě musíš dělat srandu.

String.Source: Next time, you catch 'em.
String.Dest: Next time, you catch 'em.

String.Source: Got ourselves a few new slaves for the herd.
String.Dest: Got ourselves a few new slaves for the herd.

String.Source: What the hell?
String.Dest: Co to, sakra?

String.Source: Just replenishing the staff. We go through them so quickly these days.
String.Dest: Just replenishing the staff. We go through them so quickly these days.

String.Source: That employment didn't last long.
String.Dest: That employment didn't last long.

String.Source: Well... had I known they'd never make it to Nuka-World, I would have killed them myself.
String.Dest: Well... had I known they'd never make it to Nuka-World, I would have killed them myself.

String.Source: Oh, come on now.
String.Dest: Oh, come on now.

String.Source: You need to be more convincing.
String.Dest: You need to be more convincing.

String.Source: All right. I'll be here if you're interested.
String.Dest: All right. I'll be here if you're interested.

String.Source: Oh god, I hope so. After what we've been through, a safe place is really all we want right now.
String.Dest: Oh god, I hope so. After what we've been through, a safe place is really all we want right now.

String.Source: Get outta my way.
String.Dest: Get outta my way.

String.Source: Keep up the good work, Harvey.
String.Dest: Keep up the good work, Harvey.

String.Source: We'll talk about it. It's just a lot to think about right now.
String.Dest: We'll talk about it. It's just a lot to think about right now.

String.Source: Well, I'm the Overboss, and I say you're free to go.
String.Dest: Well, I'm the Overboss, and I say you're free to go.

String.Source: We're on our way to Diamond City. Some traders we ran into told us about it.
String.Dest: We're on our way to Diamond City. Some traders we ran into told us about it.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. Maybe someday I'll learn that lesson, but for now, I guess I'm stuck here.
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. Maybe someday I'll learn that lesson, but for now, I guess I'm stuck here.

String.Source: Diamond City is great. You guys will really like it there.
String.Dest: Diamond City is great. You guys will really like it there.

String.Source: It's just... Colter could barely lug his ass out of his den, let alone Nuka-World. Been a long time since anyone of importance came all this way.
String.Dest: It's just... Colter could barely lug his ass out of his den, let alone Nuka-World. Been a long time since anyone of importance came all this way.

String.Source: I'm just saying I'm tired. I'm down with doing whatever it takes to live to see another day.
String.Dest: I'm just saying I'm tired. I'm down with doing whatever it takes to live to see another day.

String.Source: It's not everyday I get to hear good news. Let me know if you're up for trading.
String.Dest: It's not everyday I get to hear good news. Let me know if you're up for trading.

String.Source: You... You're serious, aren't you? I ain't gonna say no, and believe me, it'll be a cold day in hell if you see me in the Commonwealth again.
String.Dest: You... You're serious, aren't you? I ain't gonna say no, and believe me, it'll be a cold day in hell if you see me in the Commonwealth again.

String.Source: Take a look.
String.Dest: Podívej se.

String.Source: Got a little something for everyone.
String.Dest: Got a little something for everyone.

String.Source: Interested in trading now?
String.Dest: Interested in trading now?

String.Source: If you need something, Cora's got a few things for trade.
String.Dest: If you need something, Cora's got a few things for trade.

String.Source: Little bit of everything. Bunch of odds and ends we grabbed before we left and whatever we could scavenge along the way.
String.Dest: Little bit of everything. Bunch of odds and ends we grabbed before we left and whatever we could scavenge along the way.

String.Source: What do you have?
String.Dest: Co máš?

String.Source: Sorry, I'm not really good at conversation.
String.Dest: Sorry, I'm not really good at conversation.

String.Source: Actually, let me see what you got after all.
String.Dest: Actually, let me see what you got after all.

String.Source: You guys are all family?
String.Dest: You guys are all family?

String.Source: Damn it. I knew it sounded too good to be true. I guess we can always try Nuka-World... but I've heard some crazy stories about that place.
String.Dest: Damn it. I knew it sounded too good to be true. I guess we can always try Nuka-World... but I've heard some crazy stories about that place.

String.Source: Hope we don't run into ferals tonight.
String.Dest: Hope we don't run into ferals tonight.

String.Source: Chelsea's so nervous all the time. I can barely comfort her these days.
String.Dest: Chelsea's so nervous all the time. I can barely comfort her these days.

String.Source: Really? Maybe the rumors we heard weren't true then. I'll talk to the others. I think we'll give it a shot.
String.Dest: Really? Maybe the rumors we heard weren't true then. I'll talk to the others. I think we'll give it a shot.

String.Source: Are you saying you don't approve of our methods?
String.Dest: Are you saying you don't approve of our methods?

String.Source: We had a decent place to stay for a while, but every time we'd build it up, sure enough, Raiders, Gunners, you name it...
String.Dest: We had a decent place to stay for a while, but every time we'd build it up, sure enough, Raiders, Gunners, you name it...

String.Source: Sure thing.
String.Dest: Jasňačka.

String.Source: High walls, plenty of people. Sounded like a place we could finally make a home.
String.Dest: High walls, plenty of people. Sounded like a place we could finally make a home.

String.Source: If you don't go, it's your loss. Just spreading the word.
String.Dest: If you don't go, it's your loss. Just spreading the word.

String.Source: Caring is a mistake, Harv. Makes you weak.
String.Dest: Caring is a mistake, Harv. Makes you weak.

String.Source: Oh, thank God. The Raiders have my fam -- Oh, hey, boss.
String.Dest: Oh, thank God. The Raiders have my fam -- Oh, hey, boss.

String.Source: I'll keep packing 'em in and the Gauntlet can keep picking 'em off.
String.Dest: I'll keep packing 'em in and the Gauntlet can keep picking 'em off.

String.Source: Hey, I got you in there, didn't I? One way or another, I'll keep 'em coming.
String.Dest: Hey, I got you in there, didn't I? One way or another, I'll keep 'em coming.

String.Source: It sure sounds great, but I just don't know. You're the first person we've ran into that had anything good to say about it.
String.Dest: It sure sounds great, but I just don't know. You're the first person we've ran into that had anything good to say about it.

String.Source: Are you kidding? If I split, people I know get hurt. I can handle screwing over a stranger, but not people I care about.
String.Dest: Are you kidding? If I split, people I know get hurt. I can handle screwing over a stranger, but not people I care about.

String.Source: Basically, that the whole place is run by Raiders. One guy even told us they enslave people and make them wear these... shock collars.
String.Dest: Basically, that the whole place is run by Raiders. One guy even told us they enslave people and make them wear these... shock collars.

String.Source: No problem at all.
String.Dest: No problem at all.

String.Source: You're a real ray of sunshine, boss. Guess I'll see you around.
String.Dest: You're a real ray of sunshine, boss. Guess I'll see you around.

String.Source: Hey there, looking to trade?
String.Dest: Hey there, looking to trade?

String.Source: Why do you stick around and keep doing this?
String.Dest: Why do you stick around and keep doing this?

String.Source: They're all dead anyway. They just don't know it yet.
String.Dest: They're all dead anyway. They just don't know it yet.

String.Source: Here to trade? Talk to Cora.
String.Dest: Here to trade? Talk to Cora.

String.Source: Whoa, whoa. Where do you think you're... Oh, hey, boss. Didn't expect to see you out around here.
String.Dest: Whoa, whoa. Where do you think you're... Oh, hey, boss. Didn't expect to see you out around here.

String.Source: I'm so tired of being out in the open.
String.Dest: I'm so tired of being out in the open.

String.Source: And let me know if you're up for a trade before we move on.
String.Dest: And let me know if you're up for a trade before we move on.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. Go right ahead.
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. Go right ahead.

String.Source: Chelsea's my sister and Peter's her husband.
String.Dest: Chelsea's my sister and Peter's her husband.

String.Source: Get used to it. Now, carry on.
String.Dest: Get used to it. Now, carry on.

String.Source: Faking injury again?
String.Dest: Faking injury again?

String.Source: I go where I want. You got a problem with that?
String.Dest: I go where I want. You got a problem with that?

String.Source: What's going on out here?
String.Dest: What's going on out here?

String.Source: Just a little side business to keep fresh caps coming in. That and a little target practice.
String.Dest: Just a little side business to keep fresh caps coming in. That and a little target practice.

String.Source: We'll talk it over. Let me know if you're still interested in trading, though.
String.Dest: We'll talk it over. Let me know if you're still interested in trading, though.

String.Source: How do people survive out here all the time?
String.Dest: How do people survive out here all the time?

String.Source: Are you guys heading over to Nuka-World?
String.Dest: Are you guys heading over to Nuka-World?

String.Source: Sure thing, boss.
String.Dest: Sure thing, boss.

String.Source: Yeah, I guess it's all I'm good at. Since I fooled you, the gang leaders seem to think I've got some sort of special talent... suckers.
String.Dest: Yeah, I guess it's all I'm good at. Since I fooled you, the gang leaders seem to think I've got some sort of special talent... suckers.

String.Source: What have you heard about it?
String.Dest: What have you heard about it?

String.Source: Let's get back to trading.
String.Dest: Let's get back to trading.

String.Source: Our... parents were killed in the last raid. That was our sign to move on. We're hoping Diamond City will let us start over.
String.Dest: Our... parents were killed in the last raid. That was our sign to move on. We're hoping Diamond City will let us start over.

String.Source: See you around then.
String.Dest: See you around then.

String.Source: I can't wait to get to Diamond City. It's been a long time since we felt safe.
String.Dest: I can't wait to get to Diamond City. It's been a long time since we felt safe.

String.Source: Diamond City is a bust. Nuka-World is where you want to be.
String.Dest: Diamond City is a bust. Nuka-World is where you want to be.

String.Source: Nuka-World is perfectly safe. You guys would fit right in.
String.Dest: Nuka-World is perfectly safe. You guys would fit right in.

String.Source: You understand why I might've been confused, right?
String.Dest: You understand why I might've been confused, right?

String.Source: Not looking to cause any trouble.
String.Dest: Not looking to cause any trouble.

String.Source: What's next for you Cito? You want to stay here, or take your family and head out to the Wasteland?
String.Dest: What's next for you Cito? You want to stay here, or take your family and head out to the Wasteland?

String.Source: There will always be other Monsters. But you've seen the last of the ones that were here.
String.Dest: There will always be other Monsters. But you've seen the last of the ones that were here.

String.Source: This holotape is worthless, it doesn't point me to the cloning facility.
String.Dest: This holotape is worthless, it doesn't point me to the cloning facility.

String.Source: No. Stay with your family. I've got this.
String.Dest: No. Stay with your family. I've got this.

String.Source: Unless this "shiny thing" is about to sprout wings and lead me to the cloning facility, we're out of luck.
String.Dest: Unless this "shiny thing" is about to sprout wings and lead me to the cloning facility, we're out of luck.

String.Source: Is there anything I can say that will make you feel better?
String.Dest: Is there anything I can say that will make you feel better?

String.Source: You kill family! No! Cito kill you!
String.Dest: You kill family! No! Cito kill you!

String.Source: Here!
String.Dest: Tady!

String.Source: Cito strong. Cito help new friend!
String.Dest: Cito strong. Cito help new friend!

String.Source: How Cito thank new friend?
String.Dest: How Cito thank new friend?

String.Source: That hurt!
String.Dest: That hurt!

String.Source: Cito stay. Cito protect family.
String.Dest: Cito stay. Cito protect family.

String.Source: You dead!
String.Dest: You dead!

String.Source: Cito no trust anyone but new friend. Cito not share home!
String.Dest: Cito no trust anyone but new friend. Cito not share home!

String.Source: If you don't mind being gator bait, sure, tag along.
String.Dest: If you don't mind being gator bait, sure, tag along.

String.Source: Man!
String.Dest: Chlape!

String.Source: Cito remember something!
String.Dest: Cito remember something!

String.Source: Lady!
String.Dest: Dáma!

String.Source: Chris big and strong. Chris help new friend and Cito.
String.Dest: Chris big and strong. Chris help new friend and Cito.

String.Source: *Gorilla noises*
String.Dest: *gorilí zvuky*

String.Source: New friend done? No more Monsters?
String.Dest: New friend done? No more Monsters?

String.Source: Cito no like this place.
String.Dest: Cito no like this place.

String.Source: Monster!
String.Dest: Netvor!

String.Source: Follow Cito.
String.Dest: Follow Cito.

String.Source: Cito have idea!
String.Dest: Cito have idea!

String.Source: This home. This family.
String.Dest: This home. This family.

String.Source: New friend make bad joke. No worry, Cito think funny.
String.Dest: New friend make bad joke. No worry, Cito think funny.

String.Source: Cito so happy.
String.Dest: Cito so happy.

String.Source: Cito love family. New friend hurt Cito family, Cito hurt new friend!
String.Dest: Cito love family. New friend hurt Cito family, Cito hurt new friend!

String.Source: Cito angry new friend kill family. Cito sad new friend not friend anymore.
String.Dest: Cito angry new friend kill family. Cito sad new friend not friend anymore.

String.Source: You betray Cito?! You enemy now!
String.Dest: You betray Cito?! You enemy now!

String.Source: Cito never been here.
String.Dest: Cito never been here.

String.Source: You good guesser!
String.Dest: You good guesser!

String.Source: They're just gorillas, Cito. Get over it.
String.Dest: They're just gorillas, Cito. Get over it.

String.Source: You say nice thing. Cito like new friend.
String.Dest: You say nice thing. Cito like new friend.

String.Source: Cito not bait. Cito hook.
String.Dest: Cito not bait. Cito hook.

String.Source: I can't believe you couldn't handle that thing yourself.
String.Dest: I can't believe you couldn't handle that thing yourself.

String.Source: Cito strong!
String.Dest: Cito strong!

String.Source: Cito trust you. Cito like more new friends!
String.Dest: Cito trust you. Cito like more new friends!

String.Source: Cito see you kill Monster. You friend?
String.Dest: Cito see you kill Monster. You friend?

String.Source: No. Many more Monster. No stop.
String.Dest: No. Many more Monster. No stop.

String.Source: Death? Claw?
String.Dest: Death? Claw?

String.Source: Sorry Cito, I've got other friends moving into the zoo, and you'll just get in the way.
String.Dest: Sorry Cito, I've got other friends moving into the zoo, and you'll just get in the way.

String.Source: Well, it can't hurt you anymore, Cito.
String.Dest: Well, it can't hurt you anymore, Cito.

String.Source: Cito show you thing. Thing to help kill Monsters.
String.Dest: Cito show you thing. Thing to help kill Monsters.

String.Source: No worry. They not hurt you. You friend Cito mean you friend family.
String.Dest: No worry. They not hurt you. You friend Cito mean you friend family.

String.Source: And they should not be coming back. Your family's safe, Cito.
String.Dest: And they should not be coming back. Your family's safe, Cito.

String.Source: Are you kidding me? This isn't your family, these are animals.
String.Dest: Are you kidding me? This isn't your family, these are animals.

String.Source: I have a bad feeling you're going to ask me to kill more.
String.Dest: I have a bad feeling you're going to ask me to kill more.

String.Source: Cito glad new friend like family!
String.Dest: Cito glad new friend like family!

String.Source: Cito need help!
String.Dest: Cito need help!

String.Source: New friend follow Cito.
String.Dest: New friend follow Cito.

String.Source: No. Cito kill you!
String.Dest: No. Cito kill you!

String.Source: Okay, I could use the help. Follow me.
String.Dest: Okay, I could use the help. Follow me.

String.Source: Listen, Cito. You and your family have to get out of here. Mean people are coming and they might hurt you or your family.
String.Dest: Listen, Cito. You and your family have to get out of here. Mean people are coming and they might hurt you or your family.

String.Source: Cito not know. Cito confused why new friend hurt family!
String.Dest: Cito not know. Cito confused why new friend hurt family!

String.Source: Cito sad, but Cito understand. Home too dangerous now. Cito take family and go.
String.Dest: Cito sad, but Cito understand. Home too dangerous now. Cito take family and go.

String.Source: I'm sorry Cito, it was an accident.
String.Dest: I'm sorry Cito, it was an accident.

String.Source: Deal with it, you idiot. You're next.
String.Dest: Deal with it, you idiot. You're next.

String.Source: An-i-mal? Cito not know word.
String.Dest: An-i-mal? Cito not know word.

String.Source: What the heck are those things? Are they some sort of a Deathclaw?
String.Dest: Co to sakra je ty věci? To je nějaký druh párače?

String.Source: I have some friends moving in here, but if you play it cool we can all get along. Can you do that?
String.Dest: I have some friends moving in here, but if you play it cool we can all get along. Can you do that?

String.Source: Cito very small when first family die. First family look like Cito.
String.Dest: Cito very small when first family die. First family look like Cito.

String.Source: Dead man have important thing?
String.Dest: Dead man have important thing?
